    "# FB2NEP Workbook 10 – Causal Inference in Nutritional Epidemiology: Where Next?\n",
    "\n",
    "Version 0.1.0\n",
    "\n",
    "This workbook provides a conceptual introduction to **causal inference** in nutritional epidemiology. The aim is to outline the fundamental ideas that underpin modern approaches, clarify why causal reasoning is essential, and illustrate how these frameworks complement traditional regression.\n",
    "\n",
    "The emphasis here is deliberately **non-technical**: we focus on ideas rather than computation. Wherever examples are used, they draw on the synthetic FB2NEP cohort.\n"
   ]
  },
